        <desc>One of Banksy's recognisable pieces in 2006. It shows a woman dressed as a maid who is sweeping dirt under the cover of a brick wall. The piece is 
            said to represent the   western world to deal with global issues such as the AIDS epidemic as being the main issue in 2006. On Chalk Fun Road in North London.</desc>
